title: Kazuto Okada - Ibitsu Vol. 1-7 [Full][English][Ver2]
description:
**********
VERSION 2

The previous version had Volume 4 pages in the wrong order (Linux file ordering, I hate it). Also changed the order of the TOC pages for volumes 4-7. I'm still reading through it myself, so let's hope I won't notice any more mistakes further on.
**********


English scanlations of all 7 volumes (63 chapters) of Kazuto Okada's manga "Ibitsu".

Scanlation of this manga seems to have been quite a patchwork. I've tried to get the "best" version available for each chapter by searching all over the net:

Chapters 1-3 scanlated by XscansX, found by chance on some random website deep in the darkest corners of the internet.
Chapters 4-27 downloaded from mangahere.co (couldn't find any better working source). I don't know the various scanlators offhand, as they aren't credited properly there.
Chapters 28-63 scanlated by twomanscans.

All credit goes to the scanlators above (and the original artist of course). I just collected all of them into a neat package
